{"tid":808064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台料今年仍有1至3個熱帶氣旋入港500公里","createTime":"2018-09-06T05:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T14:27:59.000Z","uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"17923510afb30d07b2bb97bb3fab5113a323ab57","tid":808064,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:06:05.000Z","msg":"本港方面，天文台昨日更新2018年全年展望，預料全年總雨量介乎1,800至2,400毫米，屬正常至偏少；至於進入香港500公里範圍內的熱帶氣旋數目為5至8個，數目屬正常至偏多，兩個預測均與天文台今年3月的預測大致相同。今年已有4個熱帶氣旋進入香港500公里範圍，包括艾雲尼、格美、山神、貝碧嘉。除格美外，其餘的熱帶氣旋引致天文台須要發出熱帶氣旋警告信號，而山神在登陸減弱為低壓區後再次移到海上並增強為熱帶氣旋，引致天文台須要再發出熱帶氣旋警告信號，意味今年仍有1至3個熱帶氣旋入港500公里"},{"pid":"fdfb8c92a3db7d0f0f0592a571f67203b5d362d3","tid":808064,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:14:25.000Z","msg":"一句"},{"pid":"7bdf71e29798ddf6b25d0652c4a0c1c5a594edae","tid":808064,"uid":973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:17:31.000Z","msg":"反而今年暑假無乜風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上年連續三個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07870b01b0076375038b55fbb06739a610af28c4","tid":808064,"uid":108347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:19:07.000Z","msg":"年頭夠話打8個風啦"},{"pid":"c28a23d9ffe1dffdba3f04e7e911c4d98c27ad89","tid":808064,"uid":74009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:21:18.000Z","msg":"冇人信你呀"},{"pid":"8685eef39624a1be995b864834b4feeb1348a699","tid":808064,"uid":32577,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"07870b01b0076375038b55fbb06739a610af28c4","tid":808064,"uid":108347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:19:07.000Z","msg":"年頭夠話打8個風啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:21:29.000Z","msg":"大交合係連登仔嚟<br />\n多風=冇風<br />\n有風=冇風<br />\n冇風=真係冇風"},{"pid":"29272792aa7a0dcf2113679f3635757ad2b1030f","tid":808064,"uid":8762,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8685eef39624a1be9